## Step 6 — Create the Workflow File (The Scheduler)

This is the most important file — it tells GitHub *when* and *how* to run your bot automatically.

1. Click **"Add file"** → **"Create new file"**
2. In the filename box, type this path exactly (including the slashes):
```
.github/workflows/airdrop-bot.yml
